00:06:36.260 --> 00:06:39.260
Il faudrait peut-être amener du chocolat.

00:06:39.260 --> 00:06:41.260
D'autres réponses?

00:06:41.260 --> 00:06:43.260
Public: le shopping) DM: Le shopping.

